title: Morgan Stanley's Betsy Graseck Previews Bank Earnings
description: Betsy Graseck, Morgan Stanley global head of banks and diversified finance research, says 2026 bank earnings are largely in line with expectations. She tells Romaine Bostick and Katie Greifeld on “The Close” that estimates should rise as M&A and IPO activity accelerates. (Source: Bloomberg)
